      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new chapter. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014it\u2019s in incredible shape and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
