      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine example of the E46 platform, powered by the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit features a meticulously maintained valvetrain with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and documented rod bearing replacement for long-term mechanical synchronicity. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, coupled with a healthy M-Variable differential. The chassis is structurally sound, with a reinforced rear subframe and bushings that remain within factory deflection tolerances. Finished in original paint with consistent depth readings, this specimen retains its factory-spec suspension geometry and high-pressure braking performance. A turn-key acquisition for the enthusiast who demands mechanical transparency and peak atmospheric induction.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
