      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its deep, mirror-like factory finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery retains its original matte texture and 'new car' scent, free from any creases or wear. Every electronic feature functions flawlessly, and the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of. Accompanied by a comprehensive service history and all original keys/manuals, this is a turn-key investment for the most discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
